{"tid":1054351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"比特犬攻擊2母女　男子奮勇救人慘遭咬死","createTime":"2019-03-09T18:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T00:26:34.000Z","uid":217241,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7795604dcbc6a1cab8b90a58bd5bdf4ac74cc0a2","tid":1054351,"uid":217241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:15:03.000Z","msg":"澳洲一名40歲男子阿瑪托（Colin Amatto）為了保護一對母女，犧牲自己阻擋2隻正猛烈攻擊她們的惡犬，男子的耳朵、頭、胸和腹部有多處被咬傷，心搏停止，家屬忍痛決定拔管，「希望給他一個英雄式的送別。」<br />\n<br />\n綜合外電報導，這起惡犬襲人事件發生在雪梨西部一處郊區。1月24日，39歲的母親帶著10歲女兒衝到鄰居歐法（Daemgalo Ofa）家求救，當時兩人的手和背部都受了傷，渾身是血，原來是被2隻惡犬攻擊，其中一頭為美國史塔福郡梗犬(American Staffordshire Terriers，比特犬的一種)。<br />\n<br />\n阿瑪托為了搶救這對母女，獨自與惡犬搏鬥，結果在自宅中被咬成重傷緊急送醫，肇事的2隻狗在動物組織協助下被注射鎮靜劑，隔天實施安樂死。但阿瑪托傷勢過重，沒能撐過來，本月1日下午，阿瑪托在家人圍繞下拔管辭世，家人在網上設立了籌款頁面，希望替阿瑪托的葬禮集資。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，這2隻狗的主人是阿瑪托的30年好友莫雷（Dave Murray），案發前鄰居還曾見過阿瑪托和狗狗一起睡覺。阿瑪托的小舅子福克斯（Brendan Fox）表示，「他救了2個人，如果他沒有挺身而出，誰也不知道會有什麼後果。所以就這點來說，他是一個英雄。」<br />\n<br />\n福克斯說，家人並未因狗狗咬死阿瑪托而責怪莫雷。而莫雷的妻子表示：「他認識這些狗已經很長時間了，我們也不知道究竟發生了什麼事情。」警方目前仍在調查這起案件。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190309/1529961/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190309%2F1529961%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2Ftn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=6a3df303\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190309%2F1529961%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=a0671cbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190309/1529961/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"2c652fb432c05e155167491c6afe851c072429b4","tid":1054351,"uid":61991,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:19:13.000Z","msg":"隻狗咁撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇圖個男人都唔似弱雞呀"},{"pid":"1ae4e20f04f675c7088e3a98b4fa17688ace7157","tid":1054351,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:34:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"771e063c29dd217669423948e47326a1fe5396a0","tid":1054351,"uid":34517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ae4e20f04f675c7088e3a98b4fa17688ace7157","tid":1054351,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c652fb432c05e155167491c6afe851c072429b4","tid":1054351,"uid":61991,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:19:13.000Z","msg":"隻狗咁撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇圖個男人都唔似弱雞呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:34:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:39:59.000Z","msg":"一咬就唔放 係咁扯住 失血過多好快死"},{"pid":"f43ae40a57fd811923b396546e5714dc67227a0b","tid":1054351,"uid":187902,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:56:48.000Z","msg":"不嬲都覺得養狗都算<br />\n養pitbull之類真係仆街黎<br />\n日日話唔咬人唔咬人<br />\n一咬人個陣根本阻止唔到<br />\n睇過條片 幾個消防員射曬水槍都拉唔開兩隻pitbull"},{"pid":"5e6f04dafa65ff595a138faeec4bb1472e926a58","tid":1054351,"uid":90704,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f43ae40a57fd811923b396546e5714dc67227a0b","tid":1054351,"uid":187902,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T18:56:48.000Z","msg":"不嬲都覺得養狗都算<br />\n養pitbull之類真係仆街黎<br />\n日日話唔咬人唔咬人<br />\n一咬人個陣根本阻止唔到<br />\n睇過條片 幾個消防員射曬水槍都拉唔開兩隻pitbull"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T20:20:34.000Z","msg":"養得pit pull 就係想佢咬人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通常啲MK死窮撚最鍾意養"},{"pid":"f7d772600dd5e4a9ba9977fc17737432996a0c54","tid":1054351,"uid":197602,"like":1,"